# Presentation assets

This directory holds:
- Extracted brand-kit assets (logos, wordmarks, mood images)
- Project-specific imagery the deck uses
- Icons, charts, diagrams referenced by `SLIDE_PLAN.md`

`/bq-presentation` writes here when source material is provided or when assets are generated.

Subdirectories often used:
- `images/` — photographs, illustrations
- `icons/` — icon set (one consistent style)
- `logos/` — brand wordmarks, primary marks
- `mood/` — reference mood images
- `charts/` — chart sources (CSV / JSON / SVG)

The `outputs/` sibling directory holds the rendered presentation files (PPTX, HTML, PDF exports).
